# Controllers Layer
#
# Contains request/response handler functions, one file per domain:
#   authController.js         — register, login, requestOtp, verifyOtp
#   adminController.js        — getStats, getAllDoctors, approveDoctor, ...
#   doctorController.js       — getDoctorById, updateSlots, updateClinic, ...
#   vendorController.js       — getVendorById, updateInventory
#   appointmentController.js  — book, approve, cancel, processPayment, prescribe
#   orderController.js        — create, dispatch, receive
#   chatController.js         — send, getPartners, getConversation
#
# Rule: Controllers must contain ONLY:
#   1. Extract params/body from req
#   2. Call the corresponding service method
#   3. Return a standardized ApiResponse
#
# No DB queries. No business logic decisions. No direct sqlite3 calls.
# Populated in: Milestone 7 (Controllers)
